Package com.mariangolea.fintracker.banks.csvparser.api.transaction

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BankTransaction
    Container of both parsed and raw csv data for any transaction.
    BankTransactionAbstractGroup
    Base abstract class allowing grouping of transaction on criteria that inheritors need to support themselves.
    BankTransactionCompanyGroup
    Group of transactions which were made with the same "target" entity.
    BankTransactionDefaultGroup
    Each transaction parser uses a set of hard coded strings in order to identify transactions.
    BankTransactionUtils
    The process of parsing a set of CSV report files produces a list of BankTransactionDefaultGroup objects.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    BankTransaction.Type
    Whether a certain BankTransaction represents a incoming or outgoing operation.
